<D>__{the first thing we had to do was fix him up with that accident policy. i knew he wouldn't buy, but all i wanted was his signature on an application. so i had to make him sign without his knowing what he was signing. and i wanted a witness other than phyllis to hear me give him a sales talk. i was trying to think with your brains, keyes. i wanted all the answers ready for all the questions you were going to spring as soon as dietrichson was dead.}
<A>__{neff takes a last drag on his cigarette and kills it by running it under the ledge of the dictaphone stand. he drops the stub on the floor and resumes.}
