<D>__{a couple of nights later i went to the house. everything looked fine, except i didn't like the witness phyllis had brought in. it was dietrichson's daughter lola, and it made me feel a little queer in the belly to have her right there in the room, playing chinese checkers, as if nothing was going to happen.}
